#: ../../C/chiclet-keyboard.rst:5
msgid "chiclet keyboard"
msgstr "chiclet keyboard"

#: ../../C/chiclet-keyboard.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../C/chiclet-keyboard.rst:9
msgid ""
"A keyboard with a small, flat rectangular or lozenge-shaped rubber or "
"plastic keys that look like pieces of chewing gum. (Chiclets is the brand "
"name of a variety of chewing gum that does in fact resemble the keys of "
"chiclet keyboards.) Used esp. to describe the original IBM PCjr keyboard. "
"Vendors unanimously liked these because they were cheap, and a lot of early "
"portable and laptop products got launched using them. Customers rejected the"
" idea with almost equal unanimity, and chiclets are not often seen on "
"anything larger than a digital watch any more."
msgstr ""
"チューインガムの粒のように見える、小さく平らな長方形ないし菱形のゴムやプラスチックのキーを備えたキーボード。(Chicletsは、実際にchicletキーボードのキーに似たチューインガムの銘柄名です。)"
" 特に元のIBM "
"PCjrのキーボードを表すのに使われます。ベンダーは安価だという理由で異口同音にこれを好み、多くの初期のポータブルやラップトップ製品がこれを使って発売されました。顧客はほぼ同じく異口同音にこの考えを拒否し、chicletは今やデジタル時計より大きなものではめったに見られません。"
